@lyyprean In fact, the way to submit applications with `spark-submit` is the same, regardless of Spark 1, Spark 2 or Spark 3.
In other words, you can set `SPARK_HOME2=/path/to/spark-3.1.1-bin-hadoop2.7` in `env/dolphinscheduler_env.sh`

Note: `SPARK_HOME2` instead of `SPARK2_HOME`

@ChenCarlos You should add the following lines at the beginning of the file `include.py`:
```
#!/usr/bin/env python
# -*- coding=utf-8 -*-
```

By the way, please update the title in English, thx
